{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2014}} {{Infobox cyclist | name = Georgi Abadzhiev | image = | caption = | fullname = | birth_date = 1892 | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | discipline = | role = | ridertype = | amateurteam1 = | amateuryears1 = | proyears1 = | proteam1 = | majorwins = }}
'''Georgi Abadzhiev''' ({{lang-bg|Георги Абаджиев}}, born 1892, date of death unknown) was a Bulgarian [[cycling|cyclist]]. He competed in two events at the [[1924 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ab/georgi-abadzhiev-1.html |title=Georgi Abadzhiev Olympic Results |accessdate=12 January 2014 |work=sports-reference.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112213816/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ab/georgi-abadzhiev-1.html |archivedate=12 January 2014 |df=dmy }}</ref>
